{"tid":2183472,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]香港樂隊Dusty Bottle性感女主音 Kerryta","createTime":"2020-09-01T03:13:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T12:40:31.000Z","uid":92376,"like":60,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f94b05f28ded63a58c0dbbc25eda6b5401cb3357","tid":2183472,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/4325274-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2F4325274-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta_img_1032_688.jpg&h=51a66d4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港樂隊Dusty Bottle近來的《問世間情是何物》、《You Don't Know Me》深受本地樂迷歡迎。《Esquire》找來主音Kerryta Chau，看看這性感小美人。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau/4325321-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau%2F4325321-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=03cea090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKerryta，樂隊Dusty Bottle主音，想像中大概就是為了有型可以去到宇宙盡頭。遇到本尊。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau2/4325311-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau2%2F4325311-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=cdf46af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「幼稚園開始已經給人感覺冷酷，甚至高竇。不能否定冷酷這個形象，不笑時樣子真的蠻惡，但只是樣子，我其實很友善的，喜歡跟人聊天，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau3/4325331-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau3%2F4325331-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=7394e3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDusty Bottle由地下樂隊，到近年加盟環球音樂旗下的Brave Nusic，創作上更有計劃，面前這位，卻是最後加入的成員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau4/4325341-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau4%2F4325341-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=23a910f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「加入Dusty Bottle前我自己唱英文歌比較多。他們當時一路在找可以唱某類音樂的女主音，然後在social media看到我的報導。。。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau5/4325351-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau5%2F4325351-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=b436ef08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nKerryta加入後，樂隊推出過數首單曲，叫好叫座，隨便看音樂論壇上或看YouTube評論，樂迷形容為香港樂隊真正值得聽的音樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau6/4325361-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau6%2F4325361-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=d7e7e95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「坊間聽了我們的《You Don&rsquo;t Know Me》和《Break It Down》 可能會定位我們為復古風格，其實不是。我們想試更多不同的事。。。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau7/4325371-1-chi-HK/Dusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau7%2F4325371-1-chi-HK%2FDusty-Bottle-Kerryta-Chau_img_1032_688.jpg&h=407816ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原link<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020?utm_medium=Social-ES&amp;utm_source=Facebook#Echobox=1598868497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fdusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020%3Futm_medium%3DSocial-ES%26utm_source%3DFacebook%23Echobox%3D1598868497&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7ivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=60347d90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.esquirehk.com/people/women-we-love/dusty-bottle-kerryta-chau-2020?utm_medium=Social-ES&amp;utm_source=Facebook#Echobox=1598868497</a>"},{"pid":"b1e4198f4c9bab1cb7c85d1fecdffae891ce2c5b","tid":2183472,"uid":59852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"Ta姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfec9741cba1e0fe27044b80fb139d34a234a41","tid":2183472,"uid":60434,"like":7,"d